ygen ratio of 0.227 for the ice line planet and 0.279 for\nthe heat transition planet. These planets accreted their gas inside the ice\nline, hence the sub-solar C/O.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 30 May 2016 20:35:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 21 Jun 2016 13:46:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-02-22"}
