 present view of the circumnuclear region. There is a\npossible interesting connection between the merging state of the targets and\ndetection of microvariability.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 30 May 2016 21:38:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-07-27"}
