resses the\nformation of extra tropical Rossby waves on small planets ($R_P=1 R_{Earth}$)\nin the short rotation period regime ($P_{rot} \\leq$ 10 days).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 31 May 2016 09:36:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-06-01"}
